name: NonOropharyngealTumorsHeadAndNeck
title: Non oropharyngeal tumors head and neck
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Codes for non-oropharyngeal tumors of the head and neck; only oropharyngeal tumors of the head and neck are eligible for universal high risk HPV testing),(Data Element Scope: Includes SNOMED and ICD-10 codes for tumors of the head and neck not considered oropharyngeal in origin),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes tumors of the lip, gum, sinuses, soft tissues of the head and neck, tongue, uvula, mucosa, labial sulcus, floor and roof of mouth among others),(Exclusion Criteria: Does not include oropharyngeal tumors or brain tumors)
